{"tid":1115091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉英國打人央視記者孔琳琳　無到庭應訊　法院發拘捕令","createTime":"2019-04-19T02:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T10:39:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31808cca52260004f3192bb40c838a50a5179392","tid":1115091,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/photo_bCJLS_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fphoto_bCJLS_1200x0.png&h=e4131a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央電視台駐英記者孔琳琳，去年 9 月大鬧英國保守黨討論香港問題的座談會，涉兩度掌摑香港留學生義工 Enoch Lieu，被控普通襲擊，《BBC》報道孔琳琳未有到庭應訊，法官向她發出拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n《BBC》報道，法庭向她在英王十字區的登記記址發傳票，但孔琳琳未有到庭應訊，法官決定向她發拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n49 歲的孔琳琳，是央視駐倫敦記者，英國皇家檢控署去年底一度因為證據不足，放棄檢控她普通襲擊，但後來再次提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%AD%94%E7%90%B3%E7%90%B3-%E7%84%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%AD%E6%87%89%E8%A8%8A-%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E7%99%BC%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AD%2594%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%2590%25B3-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=6528e0c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AD%2594%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%2590%25B3-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&h=2ed9d478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%AD%94%E7%90%B3%E7%90%B3-%E7%84%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%AD%E6%87%89%E8%A8%8A-%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E7%99%BC%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"506a20cb1c7d920f723e717bcb02de8a492c8be3","tid":1115091,"uid":14103,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"希望有一日有人殺撚哂班支那人"},{"pid":"3996595fd9c826e6d4fab8d03447e7566c224345","tid":1115091,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"支那畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e863600d0ddb27ac7591e91926cd0e7563549e61","tid":1115091,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"強大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daac30b0f330abad8bb5073783fea1bba316779","tid":1115091,"uid":39855,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:47:57.000Z","msg":"上年又吹到撤銷檢控<br />\n<br />\n中央電視台記者孔琳琳，在9月底大鬧英國保守黨在伯明翰舉行的「香港自由、法治、自治受損」座談會，更涉嫌掌摑香港義工。英國警方早前以普通襲擊罪起訴她，但央視證實英國當局已撤銷起訴。<br />\n<br />\n央視發言人證實，英國檢方昨（20日）午決定對孔琳琳撤訴，孔琳琳的律師已收到檢方通知。律師表示，檢方重新審查孔琳琳被控普通襲擊罪後，認為證據不足，決定撤銷，原定今日舉行的法庭聽證亦取消。<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳是央視歐洲中心站記者，今年9月30日在英國保守黨年會一個有關香港事務的座談會上，大聲叫罵與會者「反華」和「漢奸」，並涉嫌掌摑香港留學生義工被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=da9e7d9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&h=64bf4840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475</a>"},{"pid":"7a0150c10614294058bed02f5d321dc16509eea8","tid":1115091,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"之前有晒人證物證都唔告<br />\n真係CLS"},{"pid":"34f594e217ba71e879d48b29ac721d4da4bc49e5","tid":1115091,"uid":41308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"支那無逃犯條例, 成為逃犯天堂"},{"pid":"9808cbd05c57ee61a6c289f54bdf493a239b6e46","tid":1115091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8fcadefd95d6ed42556697b47d069139f02b596a","tid":1115091,"uid":46947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"身在北京的孔琳琳：我現在很忙，不方便回應你們，bye~~"},{"pid":"abd48fdc2e44281e80c4e0415fa377446672da67","tid":1115091,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"身有屎呀？"},{"pid":"9aac232f3b9a9bbb211def2de327895125224b22","tid":1115091,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"英國狗好撚廢"},{"pid":"ebb93fd668c4555e4f67246e22e3fa2dea738db4","tid":1115091,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"返左中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79bc60780352e9e3664e39ec25b283994a98c26","tid":1115091,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:21:39.000Z","msg":"支那狗咁撚惡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8828b7f143f100aa6fa7b865c3ab1da9f42dc7e0","tid":1115091,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"咁神奇?<br />\n之前取銷檢控勁多post.<br />